about.summary: An extension to the core python logging library for logging the beginning and completion of tasks and subtasks

name: tasklogger
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "tasklogger" %}
{% set version = "0.4.2" %}

package:
  name: "{{ name|lower }}"
  version: "{{ version }}"

source:
  url: https://github.com/scottgigante/{{ name }}/archive/v{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: b56192ce11c17ac74fd70b99c97cd034877f5a663bbf740d0e15e28c10ac3f31

build:
  number: 0
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps --ignore-installed -vvv "
  noarch: python

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python
  run:
    - future
    - python

test:
  imports:
    - tasklogger

about:
  home: https://github.com/scottgigante/tasklogger
  license: GPL-2.0
  license_family: GPL
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: An extension to the core python logging library for logging the beginning and completion of tasks and subtasks

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - bebatut
